&lt;h1 id="every-theory-is-held-inside-a-physical-substrate"&gt;Every Theory Is Held Inside a Physical Substrate&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apr 12 2021&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&amp;rsquo;re always bound by the laws of physics&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt; There goes my solution for &lt;a href=""&gt;Zeno&amp;rsquo;s paradox&lt;/a&gt;, which says before you can get all the way somewhere, you have to get halfway there. And before you can get halfway there, you have to get a quarter of the way there, and therefore, you&amp;rsquo;ll never get there.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>